		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Need recommendation for a USB video capture &quot;tuner&quot</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am looking for a good video capture "tuner" that takes S-video and RCA audio or RCA composite video and audio to USB.  Basically, I want to be able to hook up my SNES to my laptop and play games on it.  So I am not really interested in recording video or watching TV.
<br />Any suggestions?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
